## Durable Lesson Protocol

After closing an incident, extract durable lessons:
1. Add to `.ai/memory/lessons-learned.json` with scope matching the incident area
2. If Second Brain configured: dual-path write to `llm-wiki/learnings/lessons/` first
3. Update `.ai/harness/ddd-ubiquitous-language.md` with any new domain terms discovered
